Package de.gmxhome.conrad.jpos.jpos_base.micr

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MICRInterface
    Interface for methods that implement property setter and method calls for the MICR device category.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data
    Class holding values for MICR data in data and error events
    Factory
    General part of MICR factory for JPOS devices using this framework.
    MICRDataEvent
    Data event implementation for MICR devices.
    MICRErrorEvent
    MICR error events, work partly similar to data events, depending on error level
    MICRProperties
    Class containing the MICR specific properties, their default values and default implementations of MICRInterface.
    MICRService
    MICR service implementation.
